### Hadith 2:395

*Narrated 'Amir bin Rabi'a:*

The Prophet said, "If any one of you see a funeral procession and he is
not going along with it, then he should stand and remain standing till
he gets behind it, or it leaves him behind, or the coffin is put down
before it goes ahead of him . "

